      content: `**Volume = Sets × Reps × Weight**

More specifically: **Hard sets per muscle per week** is what matters.

**Minimum Effective Volume:**
- 10-12 sets per muscle per week (beginners)
- 15-20 sets per muscle per week (intermediate)
- 20-25 sets per muscle per week (advanced)

**Frequency:**
How often you hit each muscle:
- 2x per week minimum for most muscles
- Spreading volume across the week > cramming into one day

**Example:**
- 16 sets of chest per week
- Better as 8 sets × 2 days than 16 sets × 1 day

**Why Frequency Matters:**
- Muscle protein synthesis peaks 24-48 hours post-workout
- Hitting muscle 2x per week = more growth signals`,
